											</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>For the record: I don&#8217;t think that we need any kind of work requirement, in large part because I think it&#8217;s a myth that people are only productive under immediate pecuniary incentive. I think there will be a lot of <i>work</i> done by people who don&#8217;t do it for their <i>job</i> in the conventional sense.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

