			<article id="div-comment-4268" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/01b656ad9bf0f8a2cc0a0c2660c6b8c7?s=74&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D74&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-74 photo' height='74' width='74' />						<b class="fn">Vin</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="http://fredrikdeboer.com/2014/02/01/online-education-and-the-desperate-need-for-educational-realism/#comment-4268">
							<time datetime="2014-02-05T16:03:36+00:00">
								5 February 2014 at 4:03 pm							</time>
