				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Yes, BUT, 99% can ALSO find something they can do that other people will pay, and they can do their bit too&#8230;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.morganwarstler.com/post/44789487956/guaranteed-income-choose-your-boss-the-market-based" rel="nofollow">http://www.morganwarstler.com/post/44789487956/guaranteed-income-choose-your-boss-the-market-based</a></p>
<p>The only way Guaranteed Income gets done is with a work requirement, using GI/CYB we can reaffirm free market choices &#8211; but let even the lowest amongst us have dream jobs.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

