				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Disagree &#8211; there is still an incentive to work even if it is not required &#8211; provided that people continue to feel incentivized by material wealth (or simply the act of labor, which, in moderation is inherently rewarding). So let&#8217;s give people the freedom to do what they want with their lives  whether or not they satisfy popular conceptions of &#8216;work&#8217; or &#8216;productivity&#8217;.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

