					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="http://fredrikdeboer.com/2014/02/01/online-education-and-the-desperate-need-for-educational-realism/#comment-20963">
							<time datetime="2014-06-06T17:51:58+00:00">
								6 June 2014 at 5:51 pm							</time>
