									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>You could also make the analogy to exercise. Online classes are comparable to to home exercise equipment, which is rusting in homes across the country. Just like autodidacts, there are a minority who will use them regularly. But to get into competitive shape, few people can do it without a personal coach. In this case, there is also a very broad range of abilities, and those who are in poor shape will require more attention.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

